# Joern Integration - Quick Win Plan (v4)

This plan adopts a **Hybrid "Side-by-Side" Approach**. Instead of replacing the legacy AST parser, we integrate Joern as an enhancement layer to provide deep data-flow insights while maintaining current stability.

## User Review Required

> [!TIP]
> **Minimal Risk**: AST analysis remains the source of truth for repository structure. Joern is added as an optional enhancement.
> **Visible Milestones**: Each phase produces a tangible artifact (HTML visualization, baseline report, or enhanced docs).

